setIncludeFriedOf

public void setIncludeFriedOf(boolean includeFriedOf)
(Optional) If set to true, you will also get back the info from the "friendof" mode. Some clients show friends and friendof data in separate tabs/panes. If you're always going to load both, then use this flag (as opposed to a tabbed dialog approach, where the user may not go to the second tab and thus would not need to load the friendof data.) friendof request variables can be used
